attributes.Long form description: First, the student removes the wheels from the rolling cart. After that, the student unscrews the bolts to remove the trays. Then, the student disassembles the trays from the rolling cart. Next, the student disassembles the side bars and unscrews them with a screwdriver from the base frames. Then, the student disassembles the base frames. Lastly, the student unscrews and disassembles the side bars.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the first wheel.
The student disassembles the upper and middle grid trays.
